ta creates with required fields and defaults\n92:   - File: `cmd/cli/tests/test_metadata_service.py:11-20`\n93:   - Verification: `pytest cmd/cli/tests/test_metadata_service.py::TestAgentMetadata::test_agent_metadata_valid -v`\n94: \n95: - [x] **T4.2**: Test AgentMetadata invalid language rejection\n96:   - Purpose: Verify ValidationError for unsupported language\n97:   - File: `cmd/cli/tests/test_metadata_service.py:22-28`\n98:   - Verification: `pytest cmd/cli/tests/test_metadata_service.py::TestAgentMetadata::test_agent_metadata_invalid_language -v`\n99: \n100: - [x] **T4.3**: Test AgentMetadata invalid build_mode rejection\n101:   - Purpose: Verify ValidationError for unsupported build_mode\n102:   - File: `cmd/cli/tests/test_metadata_service.py:30-37`\n103:   - Verification: `pytest cmd/cli/tests/test_metadata_service.py::TestAgentMetadata::test_agent_metadata_invalid_build_mode -v`\n104: \n105: - [x] **T4.4**: Test AgentMetadata port range validation\n106:   - Purpose: Verify ValidationError for port outside 1-65535 range\n107:   - File: `cmd/cli/tests/test_metadata_service.py:39-72`\n108:   - Verification: `pytest cmd/cli/tests/test_metadata_service.py::TestAgentMetadata::test_agent_metadata_invalid_port_high -v`\n109: \n110: - [x] **T4.5**: Test load_metadata from agent_metadata.yaml (primary)\n111:   - Purpose: Verify loading from primary filename\n112:   - File: `cmd/cli/tests/test_metadata_service.py:76-91`\n113:   - Verification: `pytest cmd/cli/tests/test_metadata_service.py::TestMetadataService::test_metadata_service_load_agent_metadata_yaml -v`\n114: \n115: - [x] **T4.6**: Test load_metadata fallback to agent.yaml\n116:   - Purpose: Verify fallback to second filename when primary missing\n117:   - File: `cmd/cli/tests/test_metadata_service.py:93-104`\n118:   - Verification: `pytest cmd/cli/tests/test_metadata_service.py::TestMetadataService::test_metadata_service_load_fallback_agent_yaml -v`\n119: \n120: - [x] **T4.7**: Test load_metadata fallback to 