ts)\n251: ```\n252: \n253: ---\n254: \n255: ## Verification Commands\n256: \n257: | Task | Verification Command |\n258: |------|----------------------|\n259: | T1.1 | `pytest cmd/cli/tests/test_metadata_service.py::TestAgentMetadata::test_agent_metadata_valid -v` |\n260: | T1.2 | `pytest cmd/cli/tests/test_metadata_service.py::TestAgentMetadata::test_agent_metadata_invalid_language -v` |\n261: | T1.3 | `pytest cmd/cli/tests/test_metadata_service.py::TestAgentMetadata::test_agent_metadata_invalid_build_mode -v` |\n262: | T1.4 | `pytest cmd/cli/tests/test_metadata_service.py::TestAgentMetadata::test_agent_metadata_invalid_port_low -v` |\n263: | T2.1 | `python -c \"from agentcube.models.pack_models import MetadataOptions; print('OK')\" |\n264: | T2.2 | `python -c \"from agentcube.models.pack_models import MetadataOptions; opt = MetadataOptions.from_options({'agent_name': 'test'}); print(opt.agent_name)\"` |\n265: | T3.1 | `pytest cmd/cli/tests/test_metadata_service.py::TestMetadataService::test_metadata_service_load_agent_metadata_yaml -v` |\n266: | T3.2 | `pytest cmd/cli/tests/test_metadata_service.py::TestMetadataService::test_metadata_service_load_fallback_agent_yaml -v` |\n267: | T3.3 | `pytest cmd/cli/tests/test_metadata_service.py::TestMetadataService::test_metadata_service_save_excludes_none -v` |\n268: | T3.4 | `pytest cmd/cli/tests/test_metadata_service.py::TestMetadataService::test_metadata_service_update -v` |\n269: | T3.5 | `pytest cmd/cli/tests/test_metadata_service.py::TestMetadataService::test_validate_workspace_python -v` |\n270: | T3.6 | `pytest cmd/cli/tests/test_metadata_service.py::TestMetadataService::test_validate_python_workspace_has_py -v` |\n271: | T3.7 | `pytest cmd/cli/tests/test_metadata_service.py::TestMetadataService::test_validate_java_workspace_has_pom -v` |\n272: | T4.1-T4.18 | `pytest cmd/cli/tests/test_metadata_service.py -v` |\n273: | T5.1 | `pytest cmd/cli/tests/test_pack_runtime.py::test_pack_loads_metadata -v` |\n274: | T5.2 | `py